      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, I just cut my arm really bad while cooking. its a deep one and its still oozing blood even though i put pressure on it for a while. im in cape town and dont really wanna deal with an ER trip if i dont have to... do u think i can just put some honey on it and bandage it up? i heard honey is good for healing wounds",
