      "content": "but i dont think it is that bad. its not like a spray of blood or anything, just a constant slow ooze. and i know honey helps with infection and stuff. my grandma always said honey is a natural antibiotic. if i just clean it really well and use a thick layer of honey, can i just sleep on it and see if it stops by morning? i really dont want to spend all night in a hospital waiting room.",
